This is an Annotation for Transparent Inquiry project, published by the &lt;a href="https://qdr.syr.edu"&gt;Qualitative Data Repository&lt;/a&gt;.

&lt;br/&gt;

&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font&gt;The &lt;a href="https://doi.org/10.5064/F66QRSDR"&gt;Data Overview&lt;/a&gt; discusses project context, data generation and analysis, and logic of annotation.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;

&lt;br/&gt;
Please cite as:

Moorlock, Greg. 2018. "Data for: An empirically informed analysis of the ethical issues surrounding split liver transplantation in the United Kingdom". Qualitative Data Repository. https://doi.org/10.5064/F66QRSDR


Learn more about ATI &lt;a href="https://qdr.syr.edu/ati"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.

